sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client
    participant A as API (Gin)
    participant D as DynamoDB
    participant Q as SQS (per-printer)

    C->>A: POST /jobs/:id/release {printerName}
    A->>D: GetItem(jobId)
    D-->>A: job{status: HELD}

    A->>D: UpdateItem<br/>SET status=RELEASED<br/>COND: status = HELD
    alt ConditionalCheckFailed
        D-->>A: error
        A->>D: GetItem(jobId) re-fetch
        D-->>A: current status
        A-->>C: 409 Conflict (status: X)
    else Success
        D-->>A: updated item
        A->>Q: SendMessage(jobId, s3Key)
        alt SQS fails
            Q-->>A: error
            A->>D: UpdateItem<br/>SET status=HELD<br/>COND: status = RELEASED<br/>(rollback)
            A-->>C: 500 / 503
        else SQS ok
            Q-->>A: ok
            A-->>C: 200 OK (RELEASED)
        end
    end
